4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Applied AI course that is tailored for professionals who want to leverage AI within their current roles. The course is designed to provide a deep understanding of AI and its real-world applications. Some key topics covered in the course include generative AI, context, prompts, and models. The program lasts for 6 weeks and includes 2 live, online classes per week. The class size is kept small, with a maximum of 12 students. Upon completion of the course, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. No previous experience is required to enroll in the course.

